'''Adrian Zmed''' voiced [[Cavik Toth]] in ''[[Star Wars: Jedi Starfighter]]''.

He is perhaps best known for portraying 1961 T-Bird leader Johnny Nogerelli in the 1982 musical comedy sequel, ''[[Wikipedia:Grease 2|Grease 2]]''. He also had a role the same year as LCPD Officer [[w:c:tjhooker:Vince Romano|Vince Romano]] in the TV series ''T.J. Hooker'', which starred [[w:c:memoryalpha:Star Trek: The Original Series|Star Trek]] alumni, [[w:c:memoryalpha:William Shatner|William]] [[w:c:tjhooker:William Shatner|Shatner]].

